    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is actually intentional - a series where every element occurs only once has no mode. When I was working on the code for mode I found some good sources for this, but for now at best I have the description of mode [from an applied stats course](http://www.andrews.edu/~calkins/math/edrm611/edrm03.htm#Mode):\n\n> Some data sets contain no repeated elements. In this case, there is **no mode** (or the mode is the empty set).\n"
